title: Uluru, Ayers Rock
description: In this image from the Sentinel-2A satellite, the Uluru/Ayers Rock sandstone rock formation in Australia’s Northern Territory can be seen clearly on the right. The Kata Tjuta group of domed rocks is captured in the top left.
